Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.73,0:00:07.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}今じゃ！　やれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.73,0:00:07.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}After you told me, an octopus, \Nthat I was a cool guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:20.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}フン！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:20.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm gonna save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.21,0:02:49.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もう我慢できねえ！ じかに　この目で確かめてやる！ 皆さん　落ち着いて。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.21,0:02:49.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Huh?! He vanished in an instant...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:52.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}たった今　「十老頭」と 連絡がとれました。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:52.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I can't sense him at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:57.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}中継で直接　「十老頭」から お話があります。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:57.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Only the smell of cigarettes. He's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.22,0:02:59.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}競売は間違いなく 開催されますので
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.22,0:02:59.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This isn't mere invisibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:05.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}皆さん　落ち着いて　ここ１０階の オークション会場へ　お入りください。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:05.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Does he also have the ability to change locations instantly, \Nwithout making any sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.73,0:03:09.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}大丈夫　ここは１０階だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.73,0:03:09.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That isn't possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.80,0:03:13.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}階段を降りさえしなければ いいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.80,0:03:13.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}How did he do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.21,0:03:25.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}大丈夫だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.21,0:03:25.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When I hold my breath, no one can sense my existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.72,0:03:36.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TV]　よぉ　みんな元気か？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.72,0:03:36.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You were even touching me... But your mind didn't realize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:41.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TV]　まずは連絡の不備を詫びよう すまなかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:41.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Eh? I touched you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.22,0:03:45.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TV]　だいぶ　ゴタゴタしちまったが もう大丈夫だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.22,0:03:45.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You know how some people are easily overlooked?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:49.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TV]　「幻影旅団」の頭は始末した。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:49.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When you go to a restaurant in a group, there's always one person that the \Nwaitress forgets to bring water.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.31,0:03:51.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.31,0:03:51.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This is an extreme version.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:55.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TV]　残りの連中をやるのも 時間の問題。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:55.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm right here, but no one notices me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:04:00.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TV]　狩りは玄人に任せるとして お前らは競売を楽しんでくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:04:00.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Oh... I use my other ability to turn invisible
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:05.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TV]　今夜は特別に 俺達も生で見させてもらう。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:05.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}to cover this one so no one can learn about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:10.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TV]　張り切って掘り出し物を 競り落としてくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:10.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}For the record, you and I are \Nthe only ones in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.21,0:04:13.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}皆さん　お聞きの通りです
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.21,0:04:13.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}who know this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.73,0:04:17.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「十老頭」の面々が　中継先で ご覧になっております
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.73,0:04:17.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Why tell me something so important?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:20.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}奮って競売にご参加ください。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:20.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Well, it's to build trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:05:02.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[無線]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:05:02.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Until you've done due diligence, \Ndon't trust anyone! Huh? I said it's okay, so why are \Nyou being so difficult?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.21,0:05:04.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}イルミか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.21,0:05:04.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Can you even make this decision on your own?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.21,0:05:07.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[無線] うん　俺の依頼人は？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.21,0:05:07.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What about your buddy? He'll have a fit
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:09.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ここにいる。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:09.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}when he hears you teamed up with \Na suspicious-looking monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.75,0:05:14.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うぅ。 フン！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.75,0:05:14.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And why am I insulting myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:18.20,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[無線] あっ　今　戦ってたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:18.20,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I didn't choose to be this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.20,0:05:20.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}彼は　まだ生きてる？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.20,0:05:20.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He talks a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:29.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}間一髪か　あ　よかった じゃあ　伝えといて。 「『十老頭』は始末した
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:29.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Whatever. Even a friend of twenty years \Ncould stab you in the back. Time is no measure of trust!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:33.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}約束の口座に 入金よろしく」ってね。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:33.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Say, "Ho"!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:41.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どっこいしょっと やれやれ　お互い命拾いをしたの。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:41.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You're no fun... We can never be friends. I feel the same way...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.22,0:05:43.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}やらなくていいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.22,0:05:43.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then, are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.22,0:05:45.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}わしらの依頼人は「十老頭」。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.22,0:05:45.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}About what? About teaming up with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.71,0:05:48.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その依頼人が 死んでしまった以上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.71,0:05:48.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Won't your buddy object?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.71,0:05:53.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お主は もう　ターゲットではないのでな。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.71,0:05:53.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Most likely. Because he tends to be cautious \Nand to question everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.30,0:05:58.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そう？　意外だな もうないよ　こんなチャンス。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.30,0:05:58.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This won't work, then. The deal's dead in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.22,0:06:04.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お主　わしらを快楽殺人者と 勘違いしとらんか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.22,0:06:04.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But if I insist on having my way, it'll be fine. Killua won't like it, but he'll give in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.22,0:06:06.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}好きでやっとるわけじゃなし
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.22,0:06:06.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Really... He must have a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.71,0:06:11.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}わしゃ　タダ働きも　タダ死にも まっぴらじゃわい。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.71,0:06:11.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Well, whatever. \NIf you say it's okay, I'll trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:16.70,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺が　イルミに「十老頭」の暗殺を 依頼したの　知ってたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:16.70,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So let's get to business. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.70,0:06:21.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もちろんじゃ　じゃが それはそれ　これはこれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.70,0:06:21.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I want to defeat the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.21,0:06:25.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}わしらは　受けた依頼を 遂行するだけじゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.21,0:06:25.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Want to know why? Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:26.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なるほどね。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:26.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's what I've been waiting for...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.73,0:06:30.20,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ねぇ　１つ聞いていいかい？ ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.73,0:06:30.20,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:39.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}サシでやったら　俺とあんた どっちが勝つ？ フン　そりゃ十中八九　わしじゃろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:39.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Right now, I can't tell you \Nwhy I want revenge... Okay. I'd like to know, but I'll wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:42.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お前が本気で わしをやろうと思えば
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:42.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's probably what he wants to hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:48.20,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}話は別じゃがな まったく　ナメたガキじゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:48.20,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you're that curious, I'll tell you. You'll tell me now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.20,0:06:50.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}やっぱ　バレてた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.20,0:06:50.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Just kidding! Beg all you want, but I won't tell you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.72,0:07:05.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ふぅ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.72,0:07:05.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}His name was Peggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:13.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}しんど！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:13.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I saw the King behead him right before my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.23,0:07:16.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ありゃ　盗めねえわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.23,0:07:16.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But at the time, I didn't realize \Nwhat had happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.28,0:07:23.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TEL]　じゃあ　エル病院で 待ってればいいのね？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.28,0:07:23.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You saw it happen, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:30.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}この後　救急車で　そちらへ運ぶ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:30.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Because I'd forgotten that Peggy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.21,0:07:37.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}気を失ってるだけで 心配はないが ここで寝かせておくより 病院のほうが　はるかに安全だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.21,0:07:37.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}was the one who raised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.72,0:07:54.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私も見たかったな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.72,0:07:54.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No, I should rephrase that... I've only remembered a few things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:58.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}２人が団長と どんな戦いをしたのか。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:58.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The names of my parents, my name, \Nepisodes from my childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:06.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}コルトピ 例のもの用意できるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:06.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Peggy was the name of the \NChimera Ant the King killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:12.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もちろん 生命体は無理だけど 動かないものとしてなら。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:12.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That was also my foster father's human name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.24,0:08:19.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}十分だ あとは手はず通りに。 それと…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.24,0:08:19.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He was into education, and always \Ncarried thick books around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:22.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あの娘の乗る救急車は襲うな。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:22.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In both life and death, he never \Nparted with his books about NGL.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.72,0:08:29.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}行く途中は 本当に安全なんだろうな？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.72,0:08:29.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then you all have memories \Nfrom when you were human?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:34.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もし救急車を襲う気なら 来る時に仕掛けているはずです。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:34.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I don't know if we're all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:37.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}今なら 流れ弾の心配もないでしょう。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:37.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Some Chimera Ants are clearly feral in nature. With others, there's no \Ntelling what they're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.25,0:08:42.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お待たせしました　皆様。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.25,0:08:42.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But I think I understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.30,0:08:46.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}では　これより オークションを開始いたします！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.30,0:08:46.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This is why, when we first met, \NI was willing to trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:54.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}早速　本日最初の品を ご紹介いたしましょう。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:54.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You're very human. More human than any other \NChimera Ant I've met.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:57.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ふぅ… まったく　ヒヤヒヤしたが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:57.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In fact, I'd say you're still human.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.71,0:09:01.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まぁ　終わり良ければ何とやらだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.71,0:09:01.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Really? When I met you, \NI had the opposite reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:05.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}大幹部連中には １人もケガ人は出なかったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:05.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Huh? I could sense a vicious beast inside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.22,0:09:08.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}上出来だろ おっ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.22,0:09:08.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's why I wanted to team up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:12.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}悪いな。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:12.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There's no limit to what you'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:28.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それでは 次の品をご紹介しましょう！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:28.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm Gon... Gon Freecss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:33.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ユル国宝館から持ち出された 「純金の処刑刀」！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:33.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I actually have one more ability. And the condition for its \Nactivation has been met.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:42.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それでは ２０００万からスタート！ ４０００万！ ５０００万！ はい！ ５０００万いただきました！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:42.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Time to show you my third power!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:50.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あとは自動操作で…　っと　フッ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:50.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.71,0:10:21.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}さぁ　出てまいりました 「青雲文壺」。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.71,0:10:21.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It isn't flying away...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:29.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}２億！ ３億３０００！ ３億８０００！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:29.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Does that mean I was using Perfect Plan, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:35.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おい　お前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:35.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This is my third power, God's Accomplice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.71,0:10:45.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}競売には参加しねえのか？ どういうことだ？ 「旅団」の頭を始末したんだ そりゃ当然だろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.71,0:10:45.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}While Perfect Plan is active, it allows \Nanyone I touch to use it, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:49.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そんな…　まさか…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:49.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Do you understand how powerful \Nthis technique is now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:55.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}今は残党狩りだとよ。 やっぱ　プロは違うねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:55.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This power will let us approach \Nand attack the enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.70,0:10:59.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}フフフ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.70,0:10:59.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}without their knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:07.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}役立たずの　おめぇらが 救急車だ何だと騒いでる間に ゾルディックの連中が 片付けてくれたぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:07.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The King's strength doesn't matter... If we can sneak up and use a powerful \Nattack when his guard is lowered, we'll win.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.21,0:11:10.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}…ってなわけで てめぇも　もう用なしだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.21,0:11:10.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hey, Gon...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.71,0:11:14.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}占い女のケツに ひっついとけよ　ボケが。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.71,0:11:14.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You're the partner I've been looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:22.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}とっとと　病院でもホテルでも 行っちまえ　あぁ？ それとも　点数稼ぎに失敗して がっかり来てる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:22.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The perfect guy to smack the King with the strongest attack this world's ever seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.70,0:11:35.70,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}信じない この目で確かめるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.70,0:11:35.70,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}when you used that rock-paper-scissors thing. Those were my soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.71,0:11:51.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}こいつが頭か？ まだ若造じゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.71,0:11:51.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They were killing for sport when \NI wasn't paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:54.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ナメたまねしやがって。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:54.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They're no longer my soldiers, or even my allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:12:01.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おい！ 首から上は傷めつけるなよ ネットで顔　さらすからな。 残党の死体が見つかった！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:12:01.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Well, from their perspective, \NI'm the one who's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:04.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あ…。 おう　今　行く。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:04.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What you said about being your partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.21,0:12:08.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}全部で５体か… こいつらの身元を探れ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.21,0:12:08.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There's someone who'd be better than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.71,0:12:13.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ＤＮＡ　歯型　指紋　病気 ありとあらゆるとこに照会しろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.71,0:12:13.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You know someone? Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:15.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}首から下は　バラしても構わねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:15.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll contact him. Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.82,0:12:19.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}身元が割り出せたら 親　きょうだい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.82,0:12:19.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:24.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}親戚　恋人まで全部殺せ！ 二度とナメた野郎が 現れねえよう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:24.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And even if you end up turning on me, \NI won't blame you or regret my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.21,0:12:27.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}念入りに責めて殺すんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.21,0:12:27.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Because I watched you, spoke to you, \Nand decided to trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.70,0:12:36.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハァ　ハァ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.70,0:12:36.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But I'm not about to trust others \Njust because you trust them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:43.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ラストの品と なってしまいました！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:43.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I get your point, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.21,0:12:48.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これが　世界７大美色の１つ 「緋の眼」でございます！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.21,0:12:48.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}My life is on the line here. Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:55.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クルタ族が滅亡した今 現存するのは　わずか３６対。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:55.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Perfect Plan is not invincible. In fact, it's highly vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.24,0:12:59.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その中でも 強い緋の発色を残す絶品です！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.24,0:12:59.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I can make people ignore my existence, but I'm still right there in the same place.\NThey just don't notice me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.71,0:13:06.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それでは １億ジェニーからスタート！ １億１０００！ [TEL] １億２０００！ [TEL]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.71,0:13:06.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So their attacks can still hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:12.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}１億３０００！ [TEL] １億５０００！ [TEL] ボスですか？　クラピカです。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:12.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Knowing there's a person around with \Nmy ability, what would someone do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:16.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}申し訳ありません 私の読み違いで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:16.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They'd launch attacks in every direction. Oh, you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.26,0:13:21.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「クモ」の頭がやられ 競売が予定通り行われています。 [TEL]　何!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.26,0:13:21.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If one of those attacks hits me, \Neven by dumb luck, I'm done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.74,0:13:26.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}たった今　「緋の眼」が 競りにかけられています。 参加しますか？ [TEL]　無論だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.74,0:13:26.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I hate to admit it, but when it comes to combat, \NI'm the weakest Chimera Ant around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.71,0:13:28.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何としても落札しろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.71,0:13:28.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm on the same level as foot soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.73,0:13:30.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}予算の上限は？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.73,0:13:30.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Forget the King...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.21,0:13:33.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TEL]　ない　いくらでも構わん 競り落とせ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.21,0:13:33.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I couldn't even survive a punch \Nfrom a Squadron Leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.76,0:13:39.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}分かりました。 ３億！ さぁ　３億が出ました！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.76,0:13:39.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If I just turn invisible, \Nothers can locate me with En.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.22,0:13:42.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あとは　いいですか？ ありませんか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.22,0:13:42.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's been tested, so the other \NSquadron Leaders know this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.22,0:13:45.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}３億５０００！ お！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.22,0:13:45.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I need my enemies to believe \Nmy power to be weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.73,0:13:48.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}３億６０００！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.73,0:13:48.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They need to think En is enough to beat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.73,0:13:55.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}３億７０００！ ３億９０００！ ５億！ １０億。 うっ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.73,0:13:55.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This ability is only invincible \Nif no one knows about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.22,0:14:04.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}フフフ…。 に…　２９億!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.22,0:14:04.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Enough explaining... My point is that I don't want to \Nreveal my power to any others!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.21,0:14:09.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TEL]　ええ　殺し屋が招集された 部屋にいた　スキンヘッドの男が
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.21,0:14:09.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Not even if it's someone you trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:11.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}最後まで競って来まして…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:11.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You can see for yourself, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.23,0:14:19.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゼンジか　クソ！ 予想外の出費だ…　チクショ あの豚野郎が
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.23,0:14:19.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll call him out here without mentioning you. W-Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:21.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まぁ　いいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:21.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You can watch from a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.73,0:14:25.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}値段が上がるほど コミュニティーに入る金も多くなり
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.73,0:14:25.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hello— Yo! I've been waiting, fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.72,0:14:28.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それだけ俺の評価も上がる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.72,0:14:28.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You pulled a fast one! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:33.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ネオンの占いさえあれば すぐに取り戻せる金だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:33.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I've got lots of questions for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:43.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いや　問題ない よくやった　ご苦労。 そうとも　これは先行投資 上へ行くための
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:43.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Because of you kids, the boss \Nhad to make a move... The plan's been derailed, \Nbut I support what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.72,0:14:50.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そのためにも　ネオンの機嫌だけは 損ねないようにしなくてはな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.72,0:14:50.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Letting five million die isn't right. The boss used his power to surround the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:53.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺の切り札
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:53.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.23,0:14:55.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これからも　ずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.23,0:14:55.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That should make it harder for Neferpitou \Nto control puppets remotely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.28,0:15:03.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これさえあれば…　フフっ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.28,0:15:03.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In other words, they can't perform \Nthe selection from a distance. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.74,0:15:07.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}金など　掃いて捨てるほど 入って来る
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.74,0:15:07.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But the boss and Knov-san will be expending \Nall their energy to delay Neferpitou.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.73,0:15:18.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ノストラードファミリー様ですね 落札おめでとうございます！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.73,0:15:18.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Which means, when the operation starts, they won't be in any condition to \Ntake on any of the Royal Guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:23.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}品物は　こちらでよろしいですね？ ああ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:23.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We expect more citizens to gather \Nin the capital for the celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:10.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}てめぇ　このままで帰れると 思ってんのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:10.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What? You split up? I get it... He's been disrupting things alone. Can you call him real quick?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.22,0:16:18.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}チッ　止まれ！ 頭　吹っ飛ばすぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.22,0:16:18.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No luck. He isn't picking up...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.23,0:16:23.20,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どけ。 ふざけ…　ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.23,0:16:23.20,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I think his is off. Really? Well, keep trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:24.70,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:24.70,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We should meet up, the sooner the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.70,0:16:32.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}やめておけ 誰でもいい気分なんだ。 いぃ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.70,0:16:32.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yeah. Let's find a halfway point to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.21,0:16:35.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}別に　お前でも。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.21,0:16:35.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Here... Mandai City.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.71,0:16:40.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うぅ…　あ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.71,0:16:40.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Okay, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.73,0:16:56.20,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハァ　ハァ　ハァ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.73,0:16:56.20,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Checkmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:17:00.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あいつは　一体…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:17:00.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.76,0:17:08.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハッハッハ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.76,0:17:08.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Why didn't you resign?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:15.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}こいつら…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:15.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Don't make me repeat myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:20.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ひとが捕まってた時に 酒盛りしてたんか。 おう！　戻ったか。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:20.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The match ended twenty-two moves ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.72,0:17:23.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いやいや　ほら お前らも　飲め飲め！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.72,0:17:23.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Why did you not resign then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.24,0:17:26.81,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}アホか　俺達　未成年だっての！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.24,0:17:26.81,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Did you believe I would make a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.71,0:17:44.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おめぇら よく無事で帰って来れたな。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.71,0:17:44.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:48.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そんなにヤバい連中なのか 「幻影旅団」って。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:48.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Next, we have the national Go champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.24,0:17:54.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゼパイルさんに教わった 殺し技なんだ。 あ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.24,0:17:54.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Give me the rulebook. It may look simple at first, \Nbut it is a complex game.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.73,0:18:04.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}) )
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.73,0:18:04.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It may take more time to learn than shogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.73,0:18:18.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}経験は　時に盲点を生む。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.73,0:18:18.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Please let me leave! What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.23,0:18:25.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「旅団」攻略に　贋作のノウハウが 参考になるかもな。 そう！　贋作は　奥が深い！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.23,0:18:25.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Someone! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.22,0:18:29.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺だって　ただ　だらだら 飲んでたわけじゃないぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.22,0:18:29.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}My glasses... Silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:31.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゼパイルから いろいろと教わったのさ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:31.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You are in the King's presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:42.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん…。 行きたいんだけど　クラピカに会って 「念」を教わらなきゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:42.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The choice is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.71,0:18:45.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クラピカ？　連絡とれたのか。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.71,0:18:45.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Sit across from me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.26,0:18:48.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん　あっちからの 電話待ちなんだけどね。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.26,0:18:48.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Or die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.72,0:18:56.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あいつだって 「念」を覚えたの最近だろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.72,0:18:56.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}5.5 points. The King wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.72,0:19:00.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それでも　クラピカは 「旅団」の１人を倒してるんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.72,0:19:00.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I-It only took him ten games?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.71,0:19:02.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}マジか!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.71,0:19:02.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm t-tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.21,0:19:07.70,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ああ…　何か秘密があるはずなんだ 「念」にはさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.21,0:19:07.70,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's the only explanation for that loss! And I think I have a fever. I'm short on sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:12.70,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}経験やパワー以外の 「念」独特の強さがね。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:12.70,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And I feel dizzy... I'll give you eight hours. And any medicine you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.20,0:19:17.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}アッハ！　やった！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.20,0:19:17.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Should you lose again, I won't \Nbe interested in excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.72,0:19:22.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}パパ　ありがとう！ ウフっ　キレイ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.72,0:19:22.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Rest as if your life depends on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.30,0:19:31.70,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん　許してあげる。 そうか これでパパも　ひと安心だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.30,0:19:31.70,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm impressed by how quickly \Nyou learn these games.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.70,0:19:34.70,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ウフフフ　フフフ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.70,0:19:34.70,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I can't believe it took less than half \Nthe time you spent mastering shogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:42.20,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ご苦労だった 娘の体も大丈夫そうだから
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:42.20,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's all about learning the feel. Chess, Go, shogi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:47.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これから ホテルに戻ることにする。 あとは　明日。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:47.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They have different rules, but all three
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.30,0:19:51.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「俳優の使用済みティッシュ」を 競り落として　競売は終了だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.30,0:19:51.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}have a certain rhythm to their moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:55.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺は　明後日の午前中に ここをたつが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:55.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That means disrupting your \Nopponent's rhythm is crucial.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:59.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お前達は　しばらく 娘の買い物に付き合ってくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:59.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Once you've learned the openings, \Nyou can deduce your opponent's rhythm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.73,0:20:01.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うっ…。 えっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.73,0:20:01.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Once you know their rhythm, \Nyou need only disrupt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:13.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クラピカ　残りの競売と 買い物の付き添いは
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:13.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you've already reached that conclusion, \NI don't see the benefit of playing more games.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.71,0:20:19.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私達でやるから しばらく１人で休んだら？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.71,0:20:19.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I believe they will only bore you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.22,0:20:21.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そうか…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.22,0:20:21.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}How many remain?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:26.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}すまないが　そうさせてもらう。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:26.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This country has one more professional game. It's a board game called Gungi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.71,0:20:31.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}大丈夫か？　あいつ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.71,0:20:31.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Gungi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.70,0:20:43.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TEL]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.70,0:20:43.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The game originated in East Gorteau, and nearly all citizens know how to play. Give me the rulebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.23,0:20:45.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TEL]　もしもし　クラピカ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.23,0:20:45.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}As in chess and shogi, its goal is to trap the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.71,0:20:48.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ああ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.71,0:20:48.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But you can stack up to three pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.75,0:20:52.70,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「旅団」を止めたいと言ってたな。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.75,0:20:52.70,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}At the start, you may also freely place \Nyour pieces within your own area.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.70,0:20:57.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だが　その必要はなくなったよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.70,0:20:57.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The game has a different feel
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:21:02.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「クモ」は死んだ。 [TEL]　えっ？　どういうこと？ クラピカ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:21:02.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}due to the addition of a third dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.73,0:21:10.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TEL] うん　残念。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.73,0:21:10.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}For the past fifteen years, \Nthere have been world tournaments, and East Gorteau has yet to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.21,0:21:15.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}慰めてあげようと思ったのに。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.21,0:21:15.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Currently, they're on their third representative, \Na five-time reigning champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:20.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}マフィアンコミュニティー 大したことなかったね。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:20.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then, if I defeat this champion, \NI'll be the best in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:23.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ノブナガが　いなくても 十分だったよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:23.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A fitting way to end this recreation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.73,0:21:25.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うるせぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.73,0:21:25.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Bring them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.74,0:21:50.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クラピカは　今　言いようのない むなしさを抱えていた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.74,0:21:50.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There are six days until the selection. The King has no idea
